title: Junga
subTitle: Junga, a simple bus conductor, lives with his mother and learns that his father lost their ancestral property to Chettiyar. However, he soon turns to the life of crime to retrieve it.

title: Ruslaan
subTitle: Ruslaan, a terrorist's son, undergoes a major life change when an anti-terrorism officer adopts him. Determined to fix his bad reputation, Ruslaan becomes an intelligence agent.

title: Angrezi Mein Kehte Hain
subTitle: Yashwant, a middle-aged man, refrains from expressing his love for his wife, Kiran. As a result, their relationship develops cracks, and they decide to part ways.

title: Warning
subTitle: A group of friends go for a yacht ride to celebrate their friend's birthday. However, the party turns into a misadventure when they decide to go swimming and they encounter a dangerous predator.

title: Bangalore 560023
subTitle: A group of teenagers try to beat their longtime arch-rival from another locality in a local cricket tournament. However, betrayal and violence follows in their quest to win the coveted trophy.

title: Jaganmohini
subTitle: Prince Jagathalapradhapan and Princess Azhagu Nachiyar are to marry on an auspicious day. However, things go awry when a water demon named Mohini hinders the wedding ritual.

title: Damayanthi
subTitle: A young man struggles to pay off his father's debts and decides to visit his family's abandoned bungalow. However, he soon realises that it is haunted by a vengeful ghost.

title: Raja Huli
subTitle: Raja, the son of a wealthy landlord, helps a friend convey his love to Kaveri, who happens to be Raja's old flame. However, things get complicated when Kaveri reveals she is still in love with Raja.

title: Gully Rowdy
subTitle: A young man tries to find a balance between his love interest and friends. Meanwhile, his friends convince him to stay rowdy.

title: Stree
subTitle: In the eerie townscape of Chanderi, dressmaker Vicky falls for a mysterious woman with a supernatural aura. His heart sinks at the possibility that she might be Stree, the resentful man-hunter.

title: Harom Hara
subTitle: Subrahmanyam loses his job and faces financial ruin. In an attempt to overcome his limitations, he gets involved in the illegal arms trade, eventually becoming one of South India's notorious arms dealers.

title: ACP Shiva
subTitle: Shivakumar IPS, a corrupt police officer, joins GK, a local politician, in his immoral activities. However, when GK's brother kills his best friend, he decides to turn over a new leaf.

title: Power Unlimited
subTitle: Tirupathi, who wants to become a police officer, must pose as ACP Baldev, his lookalike, to rescue Ganguly, the brother of the Home Minister Jayavardhan.

title: Cadaver
subTitle: When two surgeons mysteriously get murdered by Vetri, a prisoner, the responsibility of locating his accomplice falls on the shoulders of a pathologist.

title: Cadaver
subTitle: When two surgeons mysteriously get murdered by Vetri, a prisoner, the responsibility of locating his accomplice falls on the shoulders of a pathologist.

title: Rudra Suryavanshi
subTitle: Gunasingam, a rich farmer, lives a humble life with his family. However, things take a turn when he falls in love with the most beautiful woman in the village.

title: Naaga
subTitle: Naaga's father works in a court and wants his son to become a lawyer. However, circumstances push Naaga into the world of politics.

title: Shimla Mirchi
subTitle: Avi writes an anonymous love letter to Naina, the love of his life. However, things go awry when it lands in her mother's hand and she thinks it is meant for her.

title: Ek Aur Gundaraj
subTitle: A police officer investigates an accident that kills a team of workers. However, things take a turn when he realises that they were murdered.

title: Bharaate
subTitle: Jagan, a local travel guide, falls in love with Radha, a tourist who visits his city. Though she leaves without saying goodbye, fate conspires to being them together again.

title: Agent Chanakya
subTitle: Arjun, a highly sought-after RAW agent, is known for his skills at catching some of the most hardened criminals. However, he falls in danger when he goes after Ibrahim Qureshi, a terrorist.

title: Rider
subTitle: As love blossoms between orphans Chinnu and Kitty, fate separates them as children. However, they grow up yearning to find each other.

title: Khatarnak Policewala
subTitle: After a priest's murder and a woman's abduction, ACP Vetrimaaran uncovers a ring linked to a fertility clinic. His investigation takes a personal turn when the conspiracy affects his own family.

title: Yodha
subTitle: After he fails to save a hijacked flight, Arun, a soldier, is suspended. When he is found onboard another hijacked flight, his intentions are questioned.

title: Rowdy Rathore
subTitle: Shiva's life takes an unexpected turn when a child mistakes him for her father. Upon learning the truth, Shiva vows to change his ways for the better.

title: Gaalodu
subTitle: After fighting with a villager's son, Raju leaves for the big city, and there he meets Shukla, a nice woman from a rich family. However, this chance meeting could change Raju's life.

title: Raaz Rangon Ka
subTitle: A teacher, smitten student and struggling filmmaker become entangled in the search for a missing teen. Their quest reveals hidden truths that threaten to upend lives.

title: Raaz Rangon Ka
subTitle: A teacher, smitten student and struggling filmmaker become entangled in the search for a missing teen. Their quest reveals hidden truths that threaten to upend lives.

title: George Reddy
subTitle: George Reddy, a student leader in Osmania University, decides to revolt against the injustice and economic inequalities in society.

title: Anjala
subTitle: The members of a family join hands to save their ancestral tea shop from being demolished, even after receiving threats from the government.

title: Madholal Keep Walking
subTitle: Madholal, a security guard, leads a content life amidst his loving family and daily-commute friends. However, his aspirations come to a grinding halt after a serious injury from an explosion.

title: Siddhartha
subTitle: Surya goes to Bangkok at his mother's request and changes his name to Siddhartha. He falls in love with Sahasra, but his mother asks him to marry the girl from his enemy's family.

title: Ruslaan
subTitle: Ruslaan, a terrorist's son, undergoes a major life change when an anti-terrorism officer adopts him. Determined to fix his bad reputation, Ruslaan becomes an intelligence agent.

title: Time Machine
subTitle: Friends Elango and Pulivetti stumble upon a time machine and exploit it for personal gain. Things take a turn when they alter a gangster's fate, leading to unforeseen and dangerous consequences.

title: Pogaru
subTitle: A local thug stands up against the atrocities committed on common people and fights to secure justice for them, thus earning the public's respect and affection.

title: Sangathamizhan
subTitle: Murugan, a happy-go-lucky young man, falls in love with the daughter of Sanjay, an industrialist. However, trouble arises when Sanjay notices that Murugan looks like a figure from his dark past.

title: Gabbar Is Back
subTitle: The city's administration wrongs Aditya, a commoner. To avenge his tragedy, he disguises himself as a vigilante, Gabbar, and teams up with honest government officers to expose the corrupt.

title: Saindhav
subTitle: A man with a traumatic past is compelled to encounter an crime boss so that he can rescue his daughter from a health problem.

title: Khaidi No. 150
subTitle: Seenu, a criminal, escapes from the prison and places his doppelganger, Shankar, in his place. However, upon learning about Shankar's noble mission, he takes up the cause himself.
